{"tid":1797781,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"防暴到觀塘apm驅散示威者 便衣警於私家車上觀賞體育台","createTime":"2019-12-25T16:57:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-26T03:25:17.000Z","uid":184679,"like":11,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"314b7b279df354f8b485aaa33cf0349ec3034369","tid":1797781,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T16:57:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://tmhk.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/16f3450f-image-2019-12-26-004437-800x445.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftmhk.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F12%2F16f3450f-image-2019-12-26-004437-800x445.jpg&h=cfecec8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n數十名示威者晚上九時許在觀塘apm商場各層聚集，高呼反修例口號表達訴求，防暴警察晚上十時前到場施放胡椒噴霧作出驅散。<br />\n<br />\n本台記者晚上十一時左右到場視察，雙方對峙情況已經完結，記者發現在商場外停泊的私家車有蒙面便衣警員，在車內以平板電腦觀看電訊盈科旗下的now Sports體育台直播，而同屬nowTV的記者月前曾被防暴警員質疑其電訊盈科員工證身份。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://tmhk.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/ae462cf7-image-2019-12-26-000021.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftmhk.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F12%2Fae462cf7-image-2019-12-26-000021.jpg&h=c2d2e387&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n攝：Jason Chan, Jason Leung<br />\n文：Kevin Li<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tmhk.org/2019/12/25/防暴到觀塘apm驅散多人-便衣警於私家車上觀賞體育/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftmhk.org%2F2019%2F12%2F25%2F%E9%98%B2%E6%9A%B4%E5%88%B0%E8%A7%80%E5%A1%98apm%E9%A9%85%E6%95%A3%E5%A4%9A%E4%BA%BA-%E4%BE%BF%E8%A1%A3%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%BC%E7%A7%81%E5%AE%B6%E8%BB%8A%E4%B8%8A%E8%A7%80%E8%B3%9E%E9%AB%94%E8%82%B2%2F&d=TvOq0m68uPCtaVYdNLQuFEYnXQRGGZgEWtwyrMN1cgk%3D&h=663a2669\" target=\"_blank\">https://tmhk.org/2019/12/25/防暴到觀塘apm驅散多人-便衣警於私家車上觀賞體育/</a>"},{"pid":"3ffd115aaf2a7137fe6c3429bdffb75763367421","tid":1797781,"uid":256495,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T16:59:54.000Z","msg":"OT錢照袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d5dc4240939755d7940c2659a933b47d2398104","ti